   <narrative xml:lang="EN">iPad for 84 students with hearing Impairment,Spain</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The consequences that suffer children with hearing disabilities at communicative level are very serious because the hearing disability prevents them from interacting with their classmates with normality, leading to situations of social and educational exclusion.  From a very early age we work the integration of deaf children with hearing children, relying on an inclusive education. Only an outstanding inclusive education can guarantee their future social and professional integration.</narrative>
  </description>
